				\begin{document}$$ {\displaystyle \begin{array}{l}Y=\sum \limits_{i=1}^{38}\frac{Y_i}{G}\times G=\sum \limits_{i=1}^{38}\frac{Y_i}{G_i}\times \frac{G_i}{G}\times G=\sum \limits_{i=1}^{38}\frac{Y_i}{E_i}\times \frac{E_i}{G_i}\times \frac{G_i}{G}\times G\\ {}\kern24.5em =\sum \limits_{i=1}^{38}{A}_i\times {C}_i\times {S}_i\times G\\ {}\kern24.5em =\sum \limits_{i=1}^{38}{I}_i\times {S}_i\times G\end{array}} $$\end{document}Y=∑i=138YiG×G=∑i=138YiGi×GiG×G=∑i=138YiEi×EiGi×GiG×G=∑i=138Ai×Ci×Si×G=∑i=138Ii×Si×G

